# User Stories

1. As a manager, I want a dashboard that shows daily sales KPIs, so I can mentor employees on ways to improve.
2. As an hr admin, I want to filter employee training results by date range, so I can provide employees with certificates of completion.
3. As an accounts receivable user, I want visual AR charts for trends so I can track progress and identify accounts that need special focus.

Constraints:
- Web-based dashboard
- Desktop-first design
